    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm a Research Intern at the
        <a href="https://cps.iisc.ac.in/">Robert Bosch Centre for Cyber-Physical Systems</a> at IISc Bengaluru,
        advised by <a href="https://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/~chiru/">Professor Chiranjib Bhattacharyya</a>.
        My work focuses on High Fidelity Image Generation, and I'm broadly interested in research
        at the intersection of text and Image/3D Modeling.
      </p>

      <p>
        I graduated from <strong>Zakir Husain College of Engineering and Technology</strong>,
